Gabriel de Gravone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabriel_de_Gravone 0 Gabriel de Gravone (French pronunciation: ​[ɡabʁijɛl d(ə) ɡʁavɔn]; 1887–1972) was a French stage actor. He acted in forty films during the silent era, as well as directing one which he also starred in.
